sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / CI Pipeline
    participant CLI as odh-cli (kubectl-odh)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OLM as OLM API (in-cluster)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant FS as Local Filesystem

    Note over User,FS: Flow 1: Lint / Upgrade Readiness Assessment (Read-Only)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli lint --target-version 3.4
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DataScienceCluster (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC with component management states
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSCInitialization (singleton)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSCI with service mesh config
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterServiceVersions (rhods-operator)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Installed RHOAI version
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ClusterVersion<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: OpenShift version
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks, InferenceServices,<br/>RayClusters, PyTorchJobs, etc.<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Workload resources (23+ API groups)
    CLI->>OLM: LIST Subscriptions (cert-manager, ServiceMesh)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OLM-->>CLI: Operator installation status
    CLI-->>User: DiagnosticResults (text/json/yaml)<br/>38 checks with severity levels

    Note over User,FS: Flow 2: Backup Export (Read + Local Write)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli backup --namespace my-ns
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST Notebooks, DSPAs by namespace<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Workload resources
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET ConfigMaps, Secrets, PVCs<br/>(dependency resolution)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Dependency resources
    CLI->>FS: Write portable YAML files<br/>(metadata stripped via JQ)
    CLI-->>User: Backup summary

    Note over User,FS: Flow 3: Kueue Migration / RHBOK (Read + Write)

    User->>CLI: rhai-cli migrate run rhbok
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET DSC (check Kueue managementState)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Current Kueue state
    CLI->>K8sAPI: GET kueue-manager-config ConfigMap<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Current ConfigMap
    CLI->>K8sAPI: UPDATE ConfigMap annotation<br/>opendatahub.io/managed=false<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Annotated ConfigMap
    CLI->>OLM: CREATE Subscription<br/>(Red Hat Build of Kueue)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    OLM-->>CLI: Subscription created
    CLI->>K8sAPI: UPDATE DSC (Kueue → Unmanaged)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: DSC updated
    loop Poll until ready (exponential backoff)
        CLI->>OLM: GET CSV status<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        OLM-->>CLI: CSV phase
    end
    CLI->>K8sAPI: LIST ClusterQueues, LocalQueues<br/>(verify integrity)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>CLI: Queue resources intact
    CLI-->>User: Migration complete
